				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I play on Saryrn and my guild is going to have a PvP event in the arena-- one which I would definitely like to win.  For a 65 mage, does anyone have a recommended lineup of spells?  So far, the essentials in my mind are--
<br />

<br />
air pet (not planning on using epic)
<br />
boV
<br />
velocity (will trade out once pet is buffed)
<br />
anull
<br />
mala
<br />
nukes?
<br />

<br />
Which nukes are most effective?  I'd love to use black steel, sun vortex but the cast time is awful and can easily make the difference between life and death.  Any recommendations?  Char?  Scars (I know bolts kind of suck depending on the situation).
<br />

<br />
Any help is appreciated.  Also, any tactics in the arena would also be nice (I think there will be both one on one and en masse melee).
<br />

<br />
Thanks!<br />_________________<br />Sage Casala, Arch Convoker of Saryrn
